data.description: Tired of swiping left? Its your lucky day! Make sure you swipe right on this Greenwood beauty that will check all the boxes- at the top of the list is being  located within Cass County - BUT is inside of Lee Summit West school district.  4 bedrooms- 3 baths- 3 car garage- Finished basement with full bath. Upon opening  the front door, you are greeted with a cozy entryway. A wide staircase guides you to an open floor plan that gently flows from the Formal dining room- to the large kitchen and finally settling in the living room with vaulted ceilings and corner fireplace. Do you like to entertain or relax at the end of a long work day? Opening  the door from the kitchen takes you out to the deck  that overlooks an oversized custom built patio with  generous built in fire pit.  Do you have furr babies? The yard already has a wood fence installed for you- bonus! Time to go back inside and see that almost all of the flooring throughout is simple to maintain with little maintenance - those with allergies will really appreciate the durability of the hard surface flooring for years to come. Whether you love laundry or detest it, one thing is for sure- it is conveniently located on the bedroom level off of the Master suite.  The Master Suite has new carpet that goes into the walk in closet then leads right into a spa like bathroom complete with double vanities and a whirlpool tub.  This charming home also is having a brand new roof put on. by the beginning of May.  Don't let someone run away with your top pick - then you have to START all OVER  again. Lets get you both off the market!
